{"tid":442480,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[只作參考]如果你係我，你地會點揀","createTime":"2017-10-20T16:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T09:43:34.000Z","uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f25188eefa6f4298c9e4a71955ddeba5776dd9e1","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"小弟年二十有二，讀food sci hd上年grad，一路打算做兩年野讀返個top up之後狗衝份CA hea一世，人生目標係搵份返工玩手機玩到放工都有12-13k既工，人工可以跟年資升就得<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊份15k五日8-6既food qa，本身對food既熱誠都還好，但返左一年左右D同事好多都話以我既口才可以試下做sales，連我阿頭都話有窿路，我想既可以去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我呢一年入面做做下又覺得而家呢間公司唔錯，同屋企半個鐘車程，仲要一程輕鐵搞掂，AL七日公司比，做夠一年多七日自己放，每年再加一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做左一年加既人工我都算滿意<br />\n<br />\n到底我應該：<br />\n讀top up入政府<br />\n轉做sales試多年<br />\n讀商既top up先做sale(應該搵返同food有關既採購/marketing個D)<br />\n繼續係度打工過世<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該睇下前景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2934d9275c52ddadca050527cdd2edc146ed552","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇緊OU有得報未"},{"pid":"7c500a0f1fdd36ab83d5b6ae77b62a2c2ffea765","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c03dff3bc48ac5899ae256bfd997e4a249ad508","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好困擾"},{"pid":"72613692a9dddac522ce0bf37c072db3edaaf13c","tid":442480,"uid":139114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"啲選項大部份都未明朗，個個人都唔同選擇架啦，點答你"},{"pid":"247db53e6a46830f84c2b1de4f10c6d39e8bfcde","tid":442480,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"後生可以試多啲<br />\n如果家庭無太多負擔的話"},{"pid":"fd53552cc6dccf541ffd77bd33d5575f33c1104b","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返份有野做既工好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc143198a8340fc6dc701be3943acbe7373b4a9","tid":442480,"uid":13878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"去多幾個旅行, 溝個當地妹, 跟住移民外國唔番黎"},{"pid":"fcc04026015eeed6d4eec4e57455cebbe22700c7","tid":442480,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去多幾個旅行, 溝個當地妹, 跟住移民外國唔番黎</blockquote><br />\n台妹好定日本妹好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個做毒撚自學左日文，而家返工唔想太悶學緊韓文，學完會考慮埋韓妹"},{"pid":"d33eb8ec6999d24ca4298cbac04351543dddec10","tid":442480,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T09:43:34.000Z","msg":"樓主 都係直接做sale<br />\n如果做做下 覺得唔岩<br />\n咪先考CA ACO囉<br />\n<br />\nTop UP無咩用 留返錢去旅行好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}